thread.title: Bain
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Bain

author: Bain
title: Bain
text:
Easy to book and pick up from Queenstown NZ. All the staff were friendly and professional at collection and drop off.
The hire vehicle was what was described and was clean and reliable.
Have done business many times with ACE NZ and will keep going back!
